FBIS3-35291 "drnes036_n_94002" FBIS-NES-94-036 Document Type:Daily Report 23 Feb 1994 LEBANON U.S. Ambassador, Delegation Meet al-Hariri, Others Israeli Warning in U.S. Message NC2002095494 Beirut Radio Lebanon in Arabic 0900 GMT 20 Feb 94 NC2002095494 Beirut Radio Lebanon Language: Arabic Article Type:BFN [Text] Dr. Amin al-Hafiz, former prime minister and chairman of the Chamber of Deputies' Foreign Affairs Committee, has stated that the message delivered by U.S. Ambassador Mark Hambley to Foreign Minister Faris Buwayz contains an Israeli warning over what is happening in southern Lebanon. Al-Hafiz stressed that if the peace process gives Israel everything it wants, then it is not a peace process but a surrender process.
